<a class="carousel-item active">
<div class="fluid-iframe">
<img alt="" class="fluid-element" data-title="疑骑电动脚踏车时打滑失控，男子跌进沟渠里。（互联网）" src="https://dss1.zbstatic1.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/06/22/E68993E6BB91E8B78CE585A5E6B0B4E6B29FEFBC88E58F96E887AAE4BA92E88194E7BD91EFBC892028229_0.jpg?2865068"/>
</div>
<div class="text-track-v1 pdt15 f14">
