</div>
</a>
</div>
</div><article class="article-body" id="article-body">
<section class="flex flex-pack-center" data-s="O9KGQ======">
<div class="adv-tag adv" data-google-query-id="CKvQ483Y7oYDFapDwgUdd-EJ4Q" id="dfp-ad-imu1"><div id="google_ads_iframe_/5908/ZB_CN/imu1/realtime/singapore_0__container__"></div></div>
</section>
<div class="article-pic-title" data-s="c7DGEYA====">
  电动脚踏车看似没有损坏 。（互联网）
 </div>
<script data-s="cpaGU======" type="text/javascript"> googletag.cmd.push(function() { googletag.display('dfp-ad-imu1'); }); </script>
<p data-s="ch3GI======">这起意外发生于星期四（6月20日）下午3时15分，地点在友诺士3道往友诺士8路的路段。</p>
<p data-s="l3BGE======">男子骑电动脚踏车，疑似在自行打滑后跌进路旁的水沟，骑士倒立卡在沟渠里，受伤送院。</p>
<p data-s="TclG4======">一般相信，男子骑着电动脚踏车时，不知何故打滑，随后整个人跌入沟渠内，上半身卡在里头。</p><img alt="" data-s="3t1HE======" height="2148" src="https://dss1.zbstatic1.com/s3fs-public/articles/2024/06/22/E68993E6BB91E8B78CE585A5E6B0B4E6B29FEFBC88E58F96E887AAE4BA92E88194E7BD91EFBC892028129_0.jpg?994" title="电动脚踏车看似没有损坏 。（互联网）" width="1600"/>
<section class="further-reading" data-s="3L1HA======">
<h4 class="mgb15 sub-title">
<div class="title">
    延伸阅读
   </div></h4>
<div class="item">
<svg fill="none" height="24" viewbox="0 0 24 24" width="24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
